page.title: 20MIGRATIONS-HUMAN AND ANIMAL
page.content: {HUMAN.}Yearly temporary migrations take place, holidaymakers, people travelling to work etc. {UNEMPLOYMENT.}Permanent migrations caused by inland unemployment result in people settling in holiday caravans and cottages,causing a rise in the school rolls of our area. {ANIMALS.}Many migrating animals are funnelled here by the narrowing Holderness Peninsula.Birds,mammals, fish and butterflies all visit. {BIRDS.}These include Fieldfares, Redwings,Starlings,Woodcock,Swallows, etc also rarities like Oriental Cuckoo, Savi's Warbler and an Osprey. {BUTTERFLIES.}Brimstone, Painted Lady and Tortoiseshell are some varieties. {MAMMALS. }Roe Deer,Otter and Badgers. {FISH.}Cod,Sea Trout and Salmon enter river.Porpoises, stranded Whales are seen much less frequently.
